{"tid":2373786,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《最後生還者 2 》總監表示有意製作《制裁者》與《惡靈戰警》的電玩遊戲！？","createTime":"2021-01-20T17:31:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T18:58:20.000Z","uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"584726b828f8229c5695e590a33fbc7330c7a3a7","tid":2373786,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T17:31:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.toy-people.com/?p=59075&amp;fbclid=IwAR39tuNKU0HbdzJT96wIQ4R0mc2jksUlj20PLKqFr8IhXxFwZ3BFABv_G-8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.toy-people.com%2F%3Fp%3D59075%26fbclid%3DIwAR39tuNKU0HbdzJT96wIQ4R0mc2jksUlj20PLKqFr8IhXxFwZ3BFABv_G-8&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia8wCZVYJieBIKSEfzXA%2FSmA%3D&h=14da1a72\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.toy-people.com/?p=59075&amp;fbclid=IwAR39tuNKU0HbdzJT96wIQ4R0mc2jksUlj20PLKqFr8IhXxFwZ3BFABv_G-8</a><br />\n<br />\n褒貶不一的頑皮狗工作室 2020 年度「鉅」作《最後生還者 2 ( The Last of Us Part II )》自發售前就話題不斷。諸如工作室副總，同時也是該遊戲製作總監 Neil Druckmann 的「不爽不要買」風波以及因為玩家反響過於劇烈而導致國外網站禁止「洗負評歪風」等不勝枚舉的事件，然而最近 Neil Druckmann 又大發豪語的表示工作室的下個遊戲目標將放在...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/161114736737.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F161114736737.jpg&h=f104eef4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n是滴你沒看錯！據本人在推特接受 Greg Miller 提問時表示，他強烈希望能為漫威知名的反英雄《制裁者 The Punisher 》與《惡靈戰警 Ghost Rider 》「量身打造」電玩遊戲，詳見推特連結，而被點名的對象也包含了在美國大受好評的日本動畫《星際牛仔 Cowboy Bebop》！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/161114827821.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F161114827821.jpg&h=ac40ee27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說回來，《制裁者》自從 2020 年 11 月起就沒有新的漫畫連載，最近又因為美國白宮的示威風波而受到影響，再加上 Neil Druckmann 的這番言論，真的只能用「雪上加霜」來形容...<br />\n<br />\n言歸正傳，自 2009 年 PS3 的《 The Punisher: No Mercy 》迄今，《制裁者》的電玩改編近乎「乏人問津」，或許 Neil Druckmann 這次的「發聲」，能讓更多人開始注意這個值得討論的反英雄也說不定？"},{"pid":"b027bb847d2011c104a426b3d7b1b92233d63582","tid":2373786,"uid":112355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T17:38:42.000Z","msg":"會唔會又政治正確 去到最後冇得殺final boss 要你原諒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ad0392d581acfc90643653461a61001f72d2b6d","tid":2373786,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T17:39:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"092a4d67b07cc08d48e0dfad681fadf5e3f9b126","tid":2373786,"uid":49853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T17:40:20.000Z","msg":"Punisher殺到最後又落唔到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f9cbf1740641547c084e209285a71d392512e48","tid":2373786,"uid":105567,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b027bb847d2011c104a426b3d7b1b92233d63582","tid":2373786,"uid":112355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T17:38:42.000Z","msg":"會唔會又政治正確 去到最後冇得殺final boss 要你原諒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T17:40:33.000Z","msg":"原諒者 Forgiver"},{"pid":"b80e3f1d30503bad5b78f86feef2bd02a20522eb","tid":2373786,"uid":210291,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T18:58:20.000Z","msg":"點解樓主你個個po都要重複po幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}